This was a very cool story and very exciting obviously

54
00:02:51,300 --> 00:02:54,050
for the band, a wonderful experiment that

55
00:02:54,050 --> 00:02:56,290
showed them that a different type of pricing

56
00:02:56,290 --> 00:02:58,500
could work in the recording industry.

